{
  "stem": "280.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were handed from a big pile of-- of clothes, which were thrown together like a mountain of clothes, we were handed a dress.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Pardon me, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "First, after the shower, we were taken into a room where we were-- our hair was cut completely.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was one of the first nightmares.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was handed a little dress, a little white cotton dress, with some red I remember, which was long.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Everything was long for me, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I-- as soon as I-- I-- we got into our block, I-- somehow I tore off a piece, and I covered my head.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Nothing was so cold as my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I shall never forget that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That shivering, my head was the worse in the cold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Again, I don't know if you could picture that, how I looked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "A young girl.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I wasn't very developed-- bald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I had freckles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But the-- the-- the misery of that shaven head is unforgettable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So firstly, but after the baths, we were shaven, and then we were handed these dresses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am sorry to tell you, it wasn't shame.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was pure suffering, misery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who could think of shame of-- or of losing your-- your crown or what?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those were not normal circumstances.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to understand, that was something, the instinct of survival, and-- and the pain and the suffering of cold, of being exposed, your head, which was never exposed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe months later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the whole confusion, we were just ripped away from our parents and from everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know what happening, except something like-- we never-- never read about something like that, not to experience or to think or to hear.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course not.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
